88
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:19,960
Hit me?

89
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,600
Challenge me?

90
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,880
Master Chu Min, I…

91
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,000
Figure it out.

92
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,440
You really like Lu Ping,

93
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,560
