133
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,600
White!

134
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,600
Give the White back to me.

135
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,330
Give it back!

136
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,680
Why did Lu Ping hear the inexplicable tunes

137
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,880
