138
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,800
Speak it out!

139
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:31,760
Speak it out!

140
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,720
Give me the rabbit.

141
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,380
