170
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,760
Qisha Institute is in Kaiyang Peak?

171
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:31,320
Yes.

172
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:34,120
After being guarded by the Master Guo Wushu,

173
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:36,520
